trans-unit.source: Your online store needs to have a proper carrier registered in PrestaShop as soon as you start shipping your products. This means sending yours parcels using your local postal service, or having a contract with a private carrier which in turn will ship your parcels to your customers. In order to have PrestaShop suggest the most adequate carrier to your customers during their order checkout process, you need to register all the carriers with which you have chosen to work.

trans-unit.source: If there is no existing module for your carrier, then you can register that carrier by hand using the information that it can provide you: shipping rates, regional zones, size and weight limits, etc. Click on the "Add new carrier" button below to open the Carrier Wizard, which will help you register a new carrier in a few steps.

trans-unit.source: The "http_referer" field is the website from which your customers arrive.

trans-unit.source: If you'd like to view all the visitors coming from Google, you can type "%google%" in this field. Alternatively, you can type "%google.fr%" if you want to view visitors coming from Google France, only.

trans-unit.source: The "request_uri" field is the URL from which the customers come to your website.
trans-unit.target: Feltet "request_uri" er den URL-adresse, som kunderne kommer fra til dit websted.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the visitor accesses a product page, the URL will be like this one: "%smusic-ipods/1-ipod-nano.html".
trans-unit.target: Hvis den besøgende for eksempel åbner en vareside, vil URL-adressen ligne den her: "%smusic-ipods/1-ipod-nano.html".

trans-unit.source: This is helpful because you can add tags or tokens in the links pointing to your website.
trans-unit.target: Det er interessant, fordi du kan tilføje nogle tags eller tokens i linkene, der peger på din webshop.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can post a link (such as "%sindex.php?myuniquekeyword" -- note that you added "?myuniquekeyword" at the end of the URL) in an online forum or as a blog comment, and get visitors statistics for that unique link by entering "%%myuniquekeyword" in the "request_uri" field.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel opslå et link (såsom "%sindex.php?myuniquekeyword" -- bemærk, at du tilføjede "?myuniquekeyword" til sidst i URL-adressen) i et onlineforum eller som en blogkommentar og få statistikker over besøgende for det entydige link ved at indtaste "%%myuniquekeyword" i feltet "request_uri".

trans-unit.source: This method is more reliable than the "http_referer" one, but there is one disadvantage: if a search engine references a page with your link, then it will be displayed in the search results and you will not only indicate visitors from the places where you posted the link, but also those from the search engines that picked up that link.
trans-unit.target: Denne metode er mere pålidelig end den med "http_referer", men der er en ulempe. Hvis en søgemaskine henviser til en side med dit link, så bliver det vist i søgeresultaterne, og du vil ikke alene angive besøgende fra de steder, hvor du opslog linket, men også dem fra søgemaskinerne, der registrerede det link.

trans-unit.source: Originally, cron is a Unix system tool that provides time-based job scheduling: you can create many cron jobs, which are then run periodically at fixed times, dates, or intervals.
trans-unit.target: Som standard, er con et Unix system værktøj som tilbyder time-baserede jobkørsler: du kan oprette mange cron jobs, hvilket kan sættes til at køre på forskellige tidspunkter.

trans-unit.source: This module provides you with a cron-like tool: you can create jobs which will call a given set of secure URLs to your PrestaShop store, thus triggering updates and other automated tasks.
trans-unit.target: Dette modul tilbyder dig et cron-lignende værktøj: du kan oprette cron jobs, hvilket vil kalde et givent sæt af sikre URL'er til din webshop som fx automatiske opdateringer af diverse informationer.

trans-unit.source: Do not forget to use an absolute URL in the target link to make it valid! The link also has to be on the same domain as the shop.
trans-unit.target: Glem ikke at bruge en absolut URL i mål-link for at gøre det gyldigt! Linket skal også være på samme domæne som din shop.

trans-unit.source: Become an e-commerce expert in leaps and bounds!
trans-unit.target: Bliv en e-handel ekspert i en fart!

trans-unit.source: With all of the great features and benefits that PrestaShop offers, it's important to keep up!
trans-unit.target: Med alle de fantastiske funktioner og fordele, som Prestashop tilbyder, er det vigtigt at følge op!

trans-unit.source: The main goal of all of the features we offer is to make you succeed in the e-commerce world. In order to accomplish this, we have created a system of badges and points that make it easy to monitor your progress as a merchant. We have broken down the system into three levels, all of which are integral to success in the e-commerce world: (i) Your use of key e-commerce features on your store; (ii) Your sales performance; (iii) Your presence in international markets.
trans-unit.target: Hovedmålet med alle vores funktioner er, at få dig til at lykkes i e-handels verdenen. For at efterkomme dette, har vi oprettet et system med badges og point, som gør det lettere at følge din udvikling som e-købmand. Vi har brudt systemet ned til tre niveauer, som alle er integreret til at lykkes i e-handels verdenen: (i) Din centrale brug af e-handels funktioner på din webshop; (ii) Dine salgsresultater; (iii) Din tilstedeværelse på det internationale marked.

trans-unit.source: The more progress your store makes, the more badges and points you earn. No need to submit any information or fill out any forms; we know how busy you are, everything is automatic!
trans-unit.target: Jo større fremskridt din webshop gør, jo flere badges og point tjener du. Du behøver ikke sende nogle informationer eller udfylde formularer: vi ved hvor travlt du har, så alting sker automatisk!

trans-unit.source: Now, with the click of a button, you will be able to see sales-enhancing features that you may be missing out on. Take advantage and check it out below!
trans-unit.target: Du kan nu, med ét klik på en knap, nu se salgsfremmende funktioner som du måske mangler. Få fordelene og tjek det ud nedenfor!

trans-unit.source: Our team is available to help. Contact us today!
trans-unit.target: Vi er klar til at hjælpe dig. Kontakt os i dag!
